Bob Simmons (stunt man) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bob_Simmons_(stunt_man) 0 Bob Simmons (Fulham, London, England, 31 March 1922 – 21 October 1987) was an English actor and stunt man, best known for his work in many British made films, most notably the James Bond series.
